{"tid":2306943,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"xbox series x 淪為模擬器 ps2 psp wii遊戲都可玩","createTime":"2020-11-30T22:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T23:34:55.000Z","uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e78cda5b692b1e3bbb21c3c2844c7e71a0f19b98","tid":2306943,"uid":52763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T22:22:05.000Z","msg":"Xbox Series X主機看起來通過模擬器在運行幾個PS2遊戲上並沒有遇到太多的麻煩。油管頻道Modern Vintage Gamer近日發布了一個視頻，展示了使用Xbox Series S主機在開發者模式下良好遊玩PS2遊戲的畫面，這些遊戲包括《Jak and Daxter》，《寂靜嶺2》，《大神》、《神之手》和《克羅諾亞（Klonoa）》等等。<br />\n<br />\n外媒表示，由於Xbox Series X和S主機都支持開發者模式，因此它們可以說是非常不錯的模擬機器。<br />\n上週Modern Vintage Gamer分享了另外一個視頻，展示了通過RetroArch模擬完美運行任天堂GameCube和Wii遊戲。<br />\nXbox Series S主機本月早些時候發售，這個更廉價的主機可能並不是享受次世代遊戲的最佳選擇，但對於那些有著大量數字遊戲和訂閱了XGP服務的玩家來說，XSS可能更適合他們。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zBbaK8JdHis\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzBbaK8JdHis&d=AMq1wuZoRE%2BfxlTDVFm3xEpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=9eeeac0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zBbaK8JdHis</a>"},{"pid":"64b2b63bf5c47fd8befdfcaa7f13d691a55b7b24","tid":2306943,"uid":188176,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T22:25:36.000Z","msg":"淪為？<br />\n未出之前已經好多人討論緊咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c45e38882cbcfb3d58d6ef19c286e2eda84940c","tid":2306943,"uid":384590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T23:30:14.000Z","msg":"有冇得當mini pc"},{"pid":"1938d3170f5f530e486252b4ca98fe207e7ba0d3","tid":2306943,"uid":292392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T23:34:55.000Z","msg":"正喎，買多部s 黎當模擬器都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}